result.name: 鴻福海鮮四季火鍋

reviews.text: Nothing gets more authentic than charcoal Claypot steamboat in the Chinese steamboat culture. This is it, those typical HK drama place where you could do both steamboat and grill at the same time. Local beef is fresh and soup base is superb. Locate in a back lane of an industrial district. A little pricey but you get the full HK feel and vibes.
Love the charole BBQ and hot pot. Amazing food in a historic place.
Hong Kong style foods, pretty good service considering where it is. Food was interesting and good.
Special experience with charcoal grilling and hotpot
A nice charcoal hotpot.

result.name: 鴻福海鮮四季火鍋

reviews.text: 有一特色就是炭爐'食物質數不新鮮、裝修極殘舊，幸好可以見食材退貨
無間道拍攝場地，火烤兩食，可以一試。😋
很特別，又可BBQ, 又可打邊爐，味道good
來無間道拍攝場景朝聖，這裡有火烤兩吃，有些店員滿親切還幫我們烤及提醒我們注意的事情，本地牛也不錯吃，不過牛丸的話雖然我本身不愛但網路上推薦說紮實Q彈，結果牛丸就是牛丸啊不會變的我還是依舊不愛，除去這個每樣都蠻好吃的（最近瘟豬敏感就沒點招牌豬骨煲惹），仲會返黎食啦！
地方殘舊， 食材普通， 價錢偏高， 如非必要， 不值得去
